$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" style="display: block; padding: 10px; z-index: 9999; background: #000; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; cursor: default">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>
<div class="alert text-center gdpr-alert bg-white text-dark" data-id="gdpr-compliance" id="gdpr-compliance" role="alert">
<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-3">
<div class="gdpr-icon color-primary">
<span class="gicon gicon-preview fa-solid fa-cookie-bite fa-xl"></span>

<div class="gdpr-message">
<p class="m-0 p-0">We use cookies to ensure you have the best browsing experience on our website. By using our site, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/terms-of-service" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a></p>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

$(function() {

		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" style="display: block; padding: 10px; z-index: 9999; background: #000; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; cursor: default">Edit Page</span>');

  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Scott Rogers","value":47},{"label":"Spencer Roland","value":105},{"label":"Melanie Wood","value":49},{"label":"Nycol Walters","value":114},{"label":"Stefan McGovern","value":112},{"label":"Noah Soltero","value":160},{"label":"Will Baker","value":150},{"label":"Xander Orejudos","value":161},{"label":"Quinton Parnell","value":142},{"label":"Anthony Owens","value":121},{"label":"Dennis Black","value":119},{"label":"John Cloud","value":136},{"label":"Martín Ramirez","value":98},{"label":"Sergio Licona","value":106},{"label":"Lucas Cash","value":107},{"label":"Jose Herrera","value":141},{"label":"Montessa Califano","value":101},{"label":"Amanda Larsen","value":102},{"label":"Joe Cheevers","value":135},{"label":"Amanda Brown","value":145},{"label":"Taylor Stewart","value":148},{"label":"Carolyn Smith","value":144},{"label":"Bailey Martindale","value":153},{"label":"Amy Sokaitis","value":130},{"label":"Jessica Kramer","value":140},{"label":"Simon Wells","value":134},{"label":"Jamie Duncan","value":133},{"label":"Alessandro Llamas","value":151},{"label":"Kendra Selle","value":81},{"label":"Dani Chang","value":152},{"label":"Joel Harvey","value":154},{"label":"Jason Quintero","value":155},{"label":"Vinessa Atterberry","value":156},{"label":"Connor Burnham","value":158},{"label":"Aryona Thomas","value":159}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script id="template-promotions" type="text/html"><!-- ko ifnot: isInitializing() -->

    <!-- ko switch -->

        <!-- ko case: ad.location.type === 'single' -->
            <!-- ko with: single -->
                <div class="ad single-ad" data-bind="css: css_class">
                    <!-- ko if: link === '' || link === '#' -->
                        <span>
                            <picture data-bind="html5Picture: picture, alt: ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title))"></picture>
                        </span>
                    <!-- /ko -->
                    <!-- ko if: link !== '' && link !== '#' -->
                        <a data-bind="
                            attr:{
                                'aria-label': ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title)), 
                                href: link, 
                                title: hover_text ? hover_text : title, 
                                target: open_in_new_window ? '_blank' : '', 
                                click: $component.trackEvent.bind($data, 'click', $data.title),
                                'tabindex' : ko.computed(function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                },
                                blur: function() {
                                    var index =

                                        model.closeMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                }
                            }

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            
                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".bnygwbpay-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".bnygwbpay").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".bnygwbpay-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.bnygwbpay');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.bnygwbpay-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
                    function setStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {

                        skipLink.style.left = '0';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='99999999';
                        skipLink.style.outlineStyle='solid';
                        skipLink.style.outlineColor='#d900ff';
                        skipLink.style.outlineWidth='5px';
                        skipLink.style.outlineOffset='0';
                        skipLink.style.transition='none';
                    }
                    function removeStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {
                        skipLink.style.left = '-99999px';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='-99999';
                    }
                </script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Laurie Franklin","value":125},{"label":"Jody Pope","value":121},{"label":"Camryn Scheuber","value":129},{"label":"Austin Hogue","value":96},{"label":"Blake Cleveringa","value":117},{"label":"Malachi Cain","value":124},{"label":"Jake White","value":107}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript">
    
    window.airgap = window.airgap || {};

    window.airgap.ready((airgap) => {
        airgap.addEventListener('consent-change', ({ detail: { consent, oldConsent, changes } }) => {
            if (
                oldConsent.purposes['Functional'] == false &&
                consent.purposes['Functional'] == true
            ) {
                airgap.setConsent(window.airgapScriptLoadEvent, {
                    Functional: false,
                });
            }
        });
    }); 

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        
        if ('airgap' in window && 'transcend' in window) {
            const cpraButton = document.getElementById('cpra_button');
            cpraButton.onclick = (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                transcend.showConsentManager({ viewState: 'AcceptAllRejectAllToggle' });
            };

            window.airgap.ready(async (airgap) => {
                //await airgap.sync();
                let userConsent = airgap.getConsent();
                console.info('airgap --> userConsent', userConsent);                
            });
        }
    });


</script>

            require(['jquery', 'headroom', 'jquery-headroom'], function($) {
                $('html').headroom({ offset: 35});
                $('.main-navigation').on('mouseenter', '.c-navigation-desktop .c-navigation__item--level-1', function() {
                    $('body').addClass('nav-dropdown-open');
                });
                $('.main-navigation').on('mouseleave', '.c-navigation-desktop .c-navigation__item--level-1', function() {
                    $('body').removeClass('nav-dropdown-open');
                });

                if ((window.sidearmComponents[2].name === 'below-header-ad-b9dd86' && window.sidearmComponents[2].data.campaigns.length) || (window.sidearmComponents[1].name === 'below-header-ad-b9dd86' && window.sidearmComponents[1].data.campaigns.length)) {
                    $('.main-content-placeholder').addClass('below-header-ad-populated');
                }
            });
        </script>
<script id="template-promotions" type="text/html"><!-- ko ifnot: isInitializing() -->

    <!-- ko switch -->

        <!-- ko case: ad.location.type === 'single' -->
            <!-- ko with: single -->
                <div class="ad single-ad" data-bind="css: css_class">
                    <!-- ko if: link === '' || link === '#' -->
                        <span>
                            <picture data-bind="html5Picture: picture, alt: ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title))"></picture>
                        </span>
                    <!-- /ko -->
                    <!-- ko if: link !== '' && link !== '#' -->
                        <a data-bind="
                            attr:{
                                'aria-label': ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title)), 
                                href: link, 
                                title: hover_text ? hover_text : title, 
                                target: open_in_new_window ? '_blank' : '', 
                                click: $component.trackEvent.bind($data, 'click', $data.title),
                                'tabindex' : ko.computed(function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                },
                                blur: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.closeMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                }
                            }

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('navigation');
register_custom_loader('search');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".bksgp3pgh-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".bksgp3pgh").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".bksgp3pgh-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.bksgp3pgh');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.bksgp3pgh-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Laura LeMasters","value":92},{"label":"Brad Hawkins","value":135},{"label":"Marla Derrick","value":2},{"label":"Erin Guidarelli","value":189},{"label":"Mark Magdaleno","value":76},{"label":"Jordan Barchus","value":154},{"label":"Derek Browne","value":153},{"label":"Dylan Swanson","value":174},{"label":"Kevin Johnson ","value":94},{"label":"Dominic Fauria","value":150},{"label":"Parker Gaddis","value":171},{"label":"Brock Johnson","value":173},{"label":"Jesse Norris","value":147},{"label":"Dave Stewart","value":188},{"label":"Nikki Johnson","value":186},{"label":"Tanya Martin","value":187},{"label":"Owen Frasier","value":163},{"label":"Kailey Sears","value":165},{"label":"Owen Frasier","value":163},{"label":"Kailey Sears","value":165},{"label":"Jeff Lukowiak","value":164},{"label":"Timur Zhivdze","value":167},{"label":"Aaron Tasker","value":183},{"label":"Glenn Rogers","value":181},{"label":"Maddy Wright","value":162},{"label":"Kennedy Engelgau","value":169},{"label":"Ciera Jones","value":175},{"label":"Bryan Blehm","value":122},{"label":"Carrigan Foster","value":197},{"label":"Owen Frasier","value":163},{"label":"Matt Scholer","value":176},{"label":"Christian Igielinski","value":178},{"label":"Billy McKinney-Mathis","value":191},{"label":"Levi Cantrell","value":195},{"label":"Owen Frasier","value":163},{"label":"Matt Scholer","value":176},{"label":"Christian Igielinski","value":178},{"label":"Billy McKinney-Mathis","value":191},{"label":"Levi Cantrell","value":195},{"label":"Brandon Hannula","value":179}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript">
    
    window.airgap = window.airgap || {};

    window.airgap.ready((airgap) => {
        airgap.addEventListener('consent-change', ({ detail: { consent, oldConsent, changes } }) => {
            if (
                oldConsent.purposes['Functional'] == false &&
                consent.purposes['Functional'] == true
            ) {
                airgap.setConsent(window.airgapScriptLoadEvent, {
                    Functional: false,
                });
            }
        });
    }); 

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        
        if ('airgap' in window && 'transcend' in window) {
            const cpraButton = document.getElementById('cpra_button');
            cpraButton.onclick = (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                transcend.showConsentManager({ viewState: 'AcceptAllRejectAllToggle' });
            };

            window.airgap.ready(async (airgap) => {
                //await airgap.sync();
                let userConsent = airgap.getConsent();
                console.info('airgap --> userConsent', userConsent);                
            });
        }
    });

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('navigation');
register_custom_loader('search');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".bgrfhnk22-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".bgrfhnk22").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".bgrfhnk22-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.bgrfhnk22');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.bgrfhnk22-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
                    function setStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {

                        skipLink.style.left = '0';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='99999999';
                        skipLink.style.outlineStyle='solid';
                        skipLink.style.outlineColor='#d900ff';
                        skipLink.style.outlineWidth='5px';
                        skipLink.style.outlineOffset='0';
                        skipLink.style.transition='none';
                    }
                    function removeStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {
                        skipLink.style.left = '-99999px';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='-99999';
                    }
                </script>

						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Kirc Roland","value":4},{"label":"Traci Hilligoss","value":5},{"label":"Justin Ford","value":54},{"label":"Mickey Polis","value":72},{"label":"Josh Smith","value":73},{"label":"Traci Fuller","value":75},{"label":"Ed Earnest","value":25},{"label":"Kurt Lupinski","value":44},{"label":"Brian Valentine","value":93},{"label":"Mike Callia","value":97},{"label":"Shane McCarroll","value":98},{"label":"Mickey Polis","value":48},{"label":"Allan Brown","value":42},{"label":"Cameron Holden","value":1144},{"label":"Chad Cramer","value":1145},{"label":"Traci Fuller","value":15},{"label":"Dave Andrew","value":31},{"label":"Troy Shorey","value":1146},{"label":"Karsyn Zaragoza","value":100},{"label":"Paige Chinchen","value":1166},{"label":"Lucas Myers","value":50},{"label":"Amanda Britt","value":91},{"label":"Paige Mace","value":1143},{"label":"Joe Chicks","value":64},{"label":"Bob Ludahl","value":65},{"label":"Harlan Cruser","value":9},{"label":"Jenna Talarico","value":94}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript">
    
    window.airgap = window.airgap || {};

    window.airgap.ready((airgap) => {
        airgap.addEventListener('consent-change', ({ detail: { consent, oldConsent, changes } }) => {
            if (
                oldConsent.purposes['Functional'] == false &&
                consent.purposes['Functional'] == true
            ) {
                airgap.setConsent(window.airgapScriptLoadEvent, {
                    Functional: false,
                });
            }
        });
    }); 

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        
        if ('airgap' in window && 'transcend' in window) {
            const cpraButton = document.getElementById('cpra_button');
            cpraButton.onclick = (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                transcend.showConsentManager({ viewState: 'AcceptAllRejectAllToggle' });
            };

            window.airgap.ready(async (airgap) => {
                //await airgap.sync();
                let userConsent = airgap.getConsent();
                console.info('airgap --> userConsent', userConsent);                
            });
        }
    });


</script>

                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.closeMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                }
                            }">

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('navigation');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".b3skmtmhh-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".b3skmtmhh").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".b3skmtmhh-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.b3skmtmhh');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.b3skmtmhh-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
                    function setStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {

                        skipLink.style.left = '0';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='99999999';
                        skipLink.style.outlineStyle='solid';
                        skipLink.style.outlineColor='#d900ff';
                        skipLink.style.outlineWidth='5px';
                        skipLink.style.outlineOffset='0';
                        skipLink.style.transition='none';
                    }
                    function removeStylesOnSkipPauseLink(skipLink) {
                        skipLink.style.left = '-99999px';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='-99999';
                    }
                </script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Barry  Carel","value":4},{"label":"John Dunn","value":3},{"label":"Laura Rosa","value":1},{"label":"Makoa  Rosa","value":2},{"label":"Steve Turcotte","value":8},{"label":"Tony Willis","value":33},{"label":"Che  Dawson","value":5},{"label":"Daimen  Crump","value":7},{"label":"Dave Denny","value":15},{"label":"Art Erholm","value":18},{"label":"Jason Holler","value":19},{"label":"Clarence  Ryan","value":16},{"label":"Skyler Roehr","value":24},{"label":"Kevin  Whitehouse","value":23},{"label":"Genevieve \"LU\"  Medeiros","value":26},{"label":"Winter  Ridgeway","value":27},{"label":"Julia  Toone","value":25},{"label":"Chris Littleman","value":10},{"label":"Russ Dickinson","value":34},{"label":"Jeff  McDonald","value":32},{"label":"Emil Swain","value":28},{"label":"Marco Monzon","value":13},{"label":"Laura Rosa","value":11},{"label":"Danielle  Mendoza","value":30},{"label":"Makoa  Rosa","value":29}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

                                'tabindex' : ko.computed(function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                },
                                blur: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.closeMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                }
                            }
                            ">

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            
                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".beq3p5sux-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".beq3p5sux").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".beq3p5sux-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.beq3p5sux');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.beq3p5sux-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

By using our site, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/terms-of-service" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a></p>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>
<script>
        window.requirejsBaseUrl = "https://cdn.prestosports.com/action/cdn/info";
    </script>
