<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" style="display: block; padding: 10px; z-index: 9999; background: #000; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; cursor: default">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

By using our site, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/terms-of-service" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a></p>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

By using our site, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/terms-of-service" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a></p>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

        window.requirejsBaseUrl = "https://cdn.prestosports.com/action/cdn/info";

    $(function() {

        if (!$(e.target).is("a")) {
            $(this).toggleClass('active');
        }
        });
    });
    })(jQuery);
    </script>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<h2>Womens’s Basketball</h2>
<link href="/CMSPages/GetCSS.aspx?stylesheetname=ContactInfoWithBioWidget.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css"/>
<div class="contactcontainer">
<h3>Head Coach</h3>
<div id="p_lt_ctl02_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl06_Transformable_WebPart_CCS_Text7_basicRepeater_ctl00_ctl00_widget1_ctl00_pnGreenBorder">
<ul class="dirwithbio">
<li class="green-border-box employee-contact">
<div class="employeephoto">
<img alt="Brittany Kennedy" onerror="this.src='/ccsglobal/media/Global/FacultyStaffDirectory/no_photo_available.png'" src="/ccsglobal/media/Global/FacultyStaffDirectory/Brittany-Kennedy-sfcc.jpg"/>
</div>
<div class="employeeinfo">
<strong>Brittany Kennedy</strong><br/>
                            Fitness Center Manager<br>
<a href="mailto:Brittany.Kennedy@sfcc.spokane.edu">Brittany.Kennedy@sfcc.spokane.edu</a><br/>
<a href="tel:509-533-3648">509-533-3648</a><br/>
<div class="sitelinks">
</div>
<div id="p_lt_ctl02_pageplaceholder_p_lt_ctl06_Transformable_WebPart_CCS_Text7_basicRepeater_ctl00_ctl00_widget1_ctl00_BasicRepeater1_ctl00_pnBio">
<div class="control">
<a aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#bio1BrittanyKennedysfcc" role="button">Bio</a>
</div>
<div aria-expanded="false" class="collapse" id="bio1BrittanyKennedysfcc" style="height: 0px;">
<p><h4><strong>Coaching Career</strong></h4>
<p>Named head coach of the Spokane Falls Community College women’s basketball program in August 2022, after spending the previous five seasons as an assistant varsity coach at Lewis and Clark High School, Spokane, WA (2017-22).</p>
<p>2023-24: In her second year, Kennedy led the Sasquatch to a 10-15 overall record, nearly doubling the program’s number of wins from last season. Three players ranked in the top 5 leaders in Northwest Athletic Conference (NWAC) statistical categories: Kennedy McCorkle 1st in FT Percentage (90.9) and 1st in 3PT Percentage (39.0), Shauna Elliot 2nd in FG Percentage (52.4), and Keely Maves 3rd in FG Percentage (52.0). Her team ranked in the top 10 among the NWAC teams statistically in FG Percentage, 3PT Percentage, and FT Percentage. Two players earned NWAC East Region recognition, with Kennedy McCorkle and Keely Maves earning Second Team honors.</p>
<p>2022-23: In her first season as head coach, with no time to recruit for the upcoming season, and with only three returning players, she was able to form a team and led the Sasquatch to a 6-17 overall record (6-10 in conference). Her team ranked in the top 10 among the NWAC Conference teams statistically in 3PT made per game, 3PT Percentage, and FT Percentage. Two players earned NWAC East Region recognition, with Madeline Gebers earning First Team honors and AJ Sobotta earning All-Defensive Team honors. Three players from her team continued their playing careers at 4-year programs.</p>
<h4><strong>Professional Playing Career (2013-15)</strong></h4>
<p>Played two seasons overseas in the top women’s league in Germany (2013-14) and Finland (2014-15).</p>
<h4><strong>College Playing Career (2008 – 2013)</strong></h4>
<p><em>As A Redshirt-Senior (2012-13 – Florida Gulf Coast)</em><br>
Awards: Preseason A-Sun All-Conference Teams | Nancy Lieberman Award Watch List | A-Sun Academic All-Conference Team | A-Sun All-Conference Teams | CollegeSportsMadness.com Postseason A-Sun All-Conference Teams.</br></p>
<p>Named the A-Sun Preseason Defensive Player of the Year...tabbed the fan’s Preseason Defensive Player of the Year in the A-Sun’s Facebook fan poll...earned A-Sun Preseason All-Conference honors…named to the initial “Players Making the Buzz” watch list for the 2013 Nancy Lieberman Award, which annually recognizes the top point guard in NCAA Division I women’s basketball and is sponsored by the Detroit Rotary Club…earned a spot on the College Sports Madness All-Atlantic Sun first team...voted A-Sun Defensive Player of the Year by the conference’s head coaches and garnered a unanimous first-team All-Atlantic Sun selection...earned the Defensive Player of the Year award at the team's end of the year banquet...played in 33 of the team’s games, making 33 starts...averaged 9.7 points, 5.0 rebounds and 5.2 assists per game...shot 49.1 percent (114-of-232) from the floor...led the team in assists and steals on 24 and 23 occasions, respectively. named to the A-Sun All-Tournament Team. She led the Eagles to the school’s first NCAA Tournament appearance as a junior after winning the A-Sun Tournament and to a berth in the WNIT as a senior when they were the A-Sun runner-up.</p>
<p><em>As a Redshirt-Junior (2011-12 – Florida Gulf Coast)</em><br>
Earned A-Sun All-Academic honors...named Defensive Player of the Year at the team’s end-of-the-year banquet … played in 25 games, making 24 starts...averaged 6.6 points, 4.8 rebounds, and 3.5 assists per game...shot 47.6 percent (59-of-124) from the floor. Led the team in assists and steals per game…ranked second in assist/turnover ratio, third in steals, and sixth in assists in the conference…her 1.7 assist/turnover ratio ranked 42nd in the nation.</br></p>
<p><em>As a Junior (2010-11)</em><br>
Sat out the 2010-11 season, after transferring from Oregon State, due to NCAA Transfer Rules.</br></p>
<p><em>As A Sophomore (2009-10 - Oregon State)</em><br>
Played in all 31 games, making six starts...averaged 2.7 points and 2.2 assists per game.</br></p>
<p><em>As A Freshman (2008-09 - Oregon State)</em><br>
Played in all 32 games...averaged 3.4 points and 2.2 rebounds per game.</br></p>
<h4><strong>High School Playing Career</strong></h4>
<p>Lettered four seasons in basketball for head coach Jim Redmon and helped guide Lewis and Clark High School (Spokane, WA) to a 106-11 record during her tenure...named to Greater Spokane League (GSL) First-Team as a senior and junior and the GSL MVP as a senior...as a senior, guided Lewis and Clark to its third straight Class 4A Washington State title (2006, 2007, 2008)...shot 49 percent from the field and finished with 259 points...as a senior, finished with 76 assists, 164 rebounds, 187 steals, and 15 blocks...named to Jack Blair All-Star Game (and was named MVP) as a senior and played in the state of Washington vs. Oregon game in 2008...as a junior, shot 49.5 percent from the field and finished with 211 steals, 102 assists, and 137 rebounds...also lettered four seasons in track and field…as a sophomore, anchored the 4x200 relay team and placed 3rd at state (2006)…as a junior, again anchored the 4x200 relay team and placed 2nd at state (2007)…competed in the 100m (PR of 12.5), 200m, the long jump (PR 18’2”)...captained the basketball and track and field teams her final two years.</p>
<h4><strong>Personal</strong></h4>
<p>Graduated from Florida Gulf Coast University (2010-13) and earned a Bachelor’s degree in Social Work. Engaged to be married in 2024 to Ira Davis, Jr. In her free time, she enjoys spending time with family, reading, and watching movies.</p>
<p> </p></p>
</div>
</div>
</br></div>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

<h3>Assistant Coaches</h3>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" style="display: block; padding: 10px; z-index: 9999; background: #000; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; position: fixed; right: 0; top: 0; cursor: default">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

<div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center gap-3">

<div class="gdpr-message">

By using our site, you acknowledge that you have read and understood our <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/privacy-policy" target="_blank">Privacy Policy</a> &amp; <a href="https://www.prestosports.com/terms-of-service" target="_blank">Terms of Service</a></p>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>
<script type="text/javascript">
$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});
</script>

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<h2 class="h5">Softball</h2>
<ul class="nav flex-column nav--sidebar">

	var input = document.getElementById("search1");
input.addEventListener("keypress", function(event) {
  // If the user presses the "Enter" key on the keyboard
  if (event.key === "Enter") {
    // Cancel the default action, if needed
	  console.log("enter pressed");
    event.preventDefault();
    // Trigger the button element with a click
    searchURL();
  }
});

  }

                        skipLink.style.left = '0';
                        skipLink.style.zIndex='99999999';
                        skipLink.style.outlineStyle='solid';

                        skipLink.style.zIndex='-99999';
                    }

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Mitch Freeman","value":58},{"label":"Sandy Leber","value":8},{"label":"Grady Tweit","value":64},{"label":"Sean Fitzgerald","value":38},{"label":"Jason Lehman","value":80},{"label":"Carl Howell","value":41},{"label":"Deb Castle","value":9},{"label":"Marielle Hinderman","value":59},{"label":"Kelly Freeman","value":72},{"label":"Daniel Graber","value":19},{"label":"Kalan Smith","value":21},{"label":"Richard Henderson","value":65},{"label":"Andy Christie","value":68},{"label":"Tony Savoy","value":10},{"label":"George Kissas","value":12},{"label":"Brooke Writer","value":70},{"label":"Kaitlyn Rosenburg","value":81},{"label":"Kaylee Lamphiear","value":77},{"label":"Kortney Hiatt","value":79},{"label":"Joe Amaral","value":51},{"label":"Kiana Keyes","value":46}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script id="template-promotions" type="text/html"><!-- ko ifnot: isInitializing() -->

    <!-- ko switch -->

        <!-- ko case: ad.location.type === 'single' -->
            <!-- ko with: single -->
                <div class="ad single-ad" data-bind="css: css_class">
                    <!-- ko if: link === '' || link === '#' -->
                        <span>
                            <picture data-bind="html5Picture: picture, alt: ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title))"></picture>
                        </span>
                    <!-- /ko -->
                    <!-- ko if: link !== '' && link !== '#' -->
                        <a data-bind="
                            attr:{
                                'aria-label': ((typeof picture.images[0] != 'undefined') ? (picture.images[0].alt) : (hover_text ? hover_text : title)), 
                                href: link, 
                                title: hover_text ? hover_text : title, 
                                target: open_in_new_window ? '_blank' : '', 
                                click: $component.trackEvent.bind($data, 'click', $data.title),
                                'tabindex' : ko.computed(function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            
                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".b45jhz3ax-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".b45jhz3ax").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".b45jhz3ax-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.b45jhz3ax');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.b45jhz3ax-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Adam Whitlatch","value":24},{"label":"Tina Woodworth","value":5},{"label":"Ellen Huff","value":129},{"label":"Garrett Stout","value":92},{"label":"Dave Deutschman","value":60},{"label":"Derek Ridgway","value":86},{"label":"Riley Grandinetti","value":64},{"label":"Lamont Swinson","value":65},{"label":"Jordan Highland","value":115},{"label":"Cam Lucero","value":131},{"label":"Heather Weber","value":128},{"label":"KylieMonet Fletcher-Gilbert","value":146},{"label":"Steve Delgado","value":126},{"label":"Bailey Wallack","value":145},{"label":"Max Bright","value":118},{"label":"Kristopher Wood","value":108},{"label":"Ray Fabien","value":62},{"label":"Ryan Nielson","value":121},{"label":"Drew Jones","value":130},{"label":"Victor Martinez","value":144},{"label":"Emma Meyer","value":117},{"label":"Danny Valencia","value":140},{"label":"Bri  Benoit","value":119},{"label":"Sandra Bullock","value":58},{"label":"Nathaniel Young","value":147},{"label":"Jason Cash","value":63},{"label":"Steve Delgado","value":127},{"label":"John Atkinson","value":141},{"label":"Emma Meyer","value":143},{"label":"Bailey Wallack","value":145},{"label":"Josh White","value":55},{"label":"Kat Sotomayor","value":136},{"label":"Kyle Smith","value":112},{"label":"Kaley Greene","value":142}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript">
    
    window.airgap = window.airgap || {};

    window.airgap.ready((airgap) => {
        airgap.addEventListener('consent-change', ({ detail: { consent, oldConsent, changes } }) => {
            if (
                oldConsent.purposes['Functional'] == false &&
                consent.purposes['Functional'] == true
            ) {
                airgap.setConsent(window.airgapScriptLoadEvent, {
                    Functional: false,
                });
            }
        });
    }); 

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        
        if ('airgap' in window && 'transcend' in window) {
            const cpraButton = document.getElementById('cpra_button');
            cpraButton.onclick = (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                transcend.showConsentManager({ viewState: 'AcceptAllRejectAllToggle' });
            };

            window.airgap.ready(async (airgap) => {
                //await airgap.sync();
                let userConsent = airgap.getConsent();
                console.info('airgap --> userConsent', userConsent);                
            });
        }
    });


</script>

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('scoreboard');
register_custom_loader('navigation');
register_custom_loader('search');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".bap02crai-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".bap02crai").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".bap02crai-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.bap02crai');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.bap02crai-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

$(function() {
	if (readCookie('adminuser')) {
		$('body').append('<span id="edit-page-btn" class="btn btn-primary shadow" style="z-index: 9999; position: fixed; right: 0; bottom: 1rem;">Edit Page</span>');
		$('#edit-page-btn').click(function() {
			url = document.location.protocol + '//' + document.location.hostname
			if (document.location.port) url += ':' + document.location.port;
			url += '/admin/content/wiki/g2g';
			url += document.location.pathname;
			window.location = url;
		});
	}
});
</script>

$(function() {
  if (window.self == window.top) {
    return;
  }
  var heroic = document.referrer.indexOf("herosports.com/");
  if (heroic > -1) {
    alert("We do not allow HERO Sports to frame our site.");
    window.top.location = window.location;
  }
});

<script src="/info/presto.cookie-handler.js"></script>
<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
        $(function() {
            var prevFocusedElem = null;
            var closeDropdown = (ddParent) => {
                ddParent.children('.dropdown-menu').removeClass('show');
                ddParent.children('.nav-link').find('[aria-expanded="true"]').attr('aria-expanded', false);
            }

            $('body').on('focusin', (e) => {
                currFocusedElem = $(e.target);

                if (prevFocusedElem) {
                    var ddParent = prevFocusedElem.closest('.nav-item.parent.dropdown');
                    // if the focus moves away from an open dropdown menu then look to hide it
                    if (ddParent.length && ddParent.find(currFocusedElem).length === 0) {
                        closeDropdown(ddParent);
                    }
                }
                prevFocusedElem = currFocusedElem;
            });

            $(document).keyup((e) => {
                if (e.key === "Escape") { // Check if the pressed key is the escape key
                    $('.nav-item.parent.dropdown').each((i, ddParent) => {
                        closeDropdown($(ddParent));
                    });
                }
            });

            if($(window).width() >= 992) {
                $('#component-navbar-split-344 ul[data-column="true"] a.nav-link').on("click", function(e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    var url = $(this).attr('href');
                    window.location.href = url;
                });
            };
        })
    </script>
</div>

<main class="site-main" id="site-main" role="main">
<div class="container p-3 my-lg-5 my-4 border shadow-sm bg-white">
<div class="page-content staff-directory">
<h1 class="page-heading">Staff Directory</h1>
<section class="staff-directory">

<script>
        $(function() {
            function onElementHeightChange(elm, callback) {
                var lastHeight = elm.clientHeight
                var newHeight;
                (function run() {
                    newHeight = elm.clientHeight;
                    if (lastHeight !== newHeight) callback();
                    lastHeight = newHeight;

                    if (elm.onElementHeightChangeTimer) {
                        clearTimeout(elm.onElementHeightChangeTimer);
                    }

                    elm.onElementHeightChangeTimer = setTimeout(run, 200);
                })();
            }

            AOS.init();
            onElementHeightChange(document.body, function(){
                AOS.refresh();
            });

        });
        $( window ).on( "load", function() {
            AOS.refresh();
        });

    </script>

<script>
    $(document).ready(function() {
        var el = $('#gdpr-compliance'); // Replace 'yourElementId' with the actual ID of your element
        var id = el.data("id") || el.attr('id');
        var gdprType = "compliance";

        var dateAux = new Date();
        var dateAuxString = dateAux.toISOString().replace('T', ' ').replace('Z', '').split('.')[0] + '.' + dateAux.getMilliseconds();

        var gdpr = $('#' + id);
        var cookieHandler = new $.PRESTO.CookieHandler();
        var cookieName = "gdpr_" + gdprType;

        if (!cookieHandler.readCookie(cookieName)) {
            gdpr.addClass("show");

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-close').click(function() {
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                return false;
            });

            gdpr.find('.gdpr-accept').click(function(e) {
                e.preventDefault();
                gdpr.removeClass("show");
                cookieHandler.createCookie(cookieName, 'p', 365);
                console.log("GDPR accepted, cookies set with current date and time:", dateAuxString);
            });
        } else {

            console.log("GDPR cookie already present.");
        }
    });
</script>

<script>
    var obj = {"start":0,"count":10,"name":"staff-below-content-1","sport_id":null,"count_breakpoints":null,"css_class":"","pinned_id":"","extra":{},"context":null,"dummy":false,"type":"ads","id":"aefbe859-577b-467d-87ef-f3a44b2606da","data":{"location":{"id":0,"title":null,"type":null,"effect":null,"fixed_image_sizes":false,"excluded_sport_ids":null,"slick":false,"dfp":false,"sidearm_dfp":false,"common_page":false,"html_template":null,"name":null,"autoplay_speed":0,"accessibility_icons":false,"sizes":null,"slick_options":null,"dfp_sizes":null},"campaigns":[],"content_id":null,"content_title":null,"content_date":null,"content_url":null,"content_image_url":null},"mode":"web"};

<ads-component params="{ id: 'aefbe859-577b-467d-87ef-f3a44b2606da' }"></ads-component>

</article>
<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Matthew Vargas","value":6},{"label":"Aaron Vaughn","value":8},{"label":"Maria Adams","value":2},{"label":"Lenin Guzman Sanchez","value":3},{"label":"Iris Rodriguez","value":1},{"label":"Pablo Rodriguez Jorge","value":5},{"label":"Adam Todd-Thomas","value":4},{"label":"Amy Dehmer","value":7},{"label":"Cade Schindele","value":9},{"label":"Braden Draggoo","value":10},{"label":"Alaina Ahrens","value":17}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            
                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".bscx3mdef-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".bscx3mdef").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".bscx3mdef-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.bscx3mdef');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.bscx3mdef-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>

<script>
				require(['jquery', 'jquery-ui'], function ($) {
					require(['sidearm-responsive'], function () {
						$(function () {
							$(window).sidearmResponsive();

							var staff = [{"label":"Ray Funk","value":1},{"label":"Brooke Rodriguez","value":25},{"label":"Bob Grimes","value":1071},{"label":"Ben Krueger","value":1060},{"label":"Gunnar Ueda-Pancheri","value":1070},{"label":"Ryan  Isler","value":1069},{"label":"Von Ferguson","value":1067},{"label":"London Wilson","value":3},{"label":"Alix Harris","value":1068},{"label":"Robin Andrea","value":54},{"label":"Haley Wammock","value":1064},{"label":"Josh Vega","value":1062},{"label":"Chris Kirby","value":55},{"label":"Jason Weatherley","value":1065},{"label":"Dayna Colby","value":1066},{"label":"Darci  Dekker","value":47},{"label":"Marty McCallum","value":1057},{"label":"Angel Carrizales","value":56}];

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').autocomplete({
								appendTo: '.sidearm-staff-select-search',
								source: staff,
								select: function(event, ui) {                           
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);   
									$(this).data('ui-autocomplete').search();
								},
								focus: function(event, ui) { 
									event.preventDefault(); 
									$(this).val(ui.item.label);
								}
							}).on("keypress", function(e) {
								if (e.keyCode == 13) {
									e.preventDefault();
									searchStaff();
								}
							});

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_keyword_search').click(function(e) {
								e.preventDefault();                        
								searchStaff(); 
							});

							function searchStaff() {
								var _list = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_txt_keyword_search').data('ui-autocomplete').menu.element[0];

								if (_list.children) {
									var _matches = [];
									$.each(_list.children, function(index, _item) {
										_matches.push(_item.innerText);
									});

									var _staff = staff.filter(function(_member) {
										if ($.inArray(_member.label, _matches) > -1)
											return _member;
									});

									if (_staff.length === 0) return;

									var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
									$members.addClass('hide');

									var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');
									$categories.addClass('hide');

									$.each(_staff, function(index, member) {
										var $search = $members.filter('[data-member-id=' + member.value + ']');
										$search.removeClass('hide');

										$.each($search, function(index, search) {
											var _category = $(search).data("category-id");
											$categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
										});
									}); 
								}
							}

							$('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_btn_filter_categories').click(function(e) {
                                e.preventDefault();
                                filterStaffByCategory();
                            });

                            function filterStaffByCategory(){
                                var _category = $('#ctl00_cplhMainContent_ddl_filter_categories').val();
                                var $members = $('.sidearm-staff-member');
                                var $categories = $('.sidearm-staff-category');

                                if(_category === ""){
                                    $members.removeClass('hide');
                                    $categories.removeClass('hide');
                                    return;
                                }

                                $members.addClass('hide');
                                $categories.addClass('hide');

                                $members.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                                $categories.filter('[data-category-id=' + _category + ']').removeClass('hide');
                            }
						});
					});
				});
			</script>
</main>

<script type="text/javascript">
    
    window.airgap = window.airgap || {};

    window.airgap.ready((airgap) => {
        airgap.addEventListener('consent-change', ({ detail: { consent, oldConsent, changes } }) => {
            if (
                oldConsent.purposes['Functional'] == false &&
                consent.purposes['Functional'] == true
            ) {
                airgap.setConsent(window.airgapScriptLoadEvent, {
                    Functional: false,
                });
            }
        });
    }); 

    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
        
        if ('airgap' in window && 'transcend' in window) {
            const cpraButton = document.getElementById('cpra_button');
            cpraButton.onclick = (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                transcend.showConsentManager({ viewState: 'AcceptAllRejectAllToggle' });
            };

            window.airgap.ready(async (airgap) => {
                //await airgap.sync();
                let userConsent = airgap.getConsent();
                console.info('airgap --> userConsent', userConsent);                
            });
        }
    });

                                'tabindex' : ko.computed(function() {
                                    var index = 
                                    $parents.findIndex(function(item) {
                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;
                                    });
                                    if(index < 0)
                                        return 0;

                                    var model = $parents[index];
                                    if(model.component.name != 'main-nav')
                                        return 0;
                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav')
                                        return model.isMenuOpen() ? '0' : '-1';
                                    return 0;
                                })
                            },
                            event: {
                                focus: function() {
                                    var index =

                                        return Object.keys(item).length > 0 && item.component;

                                    if (model.component.name === 'main-nav') {
                                        model.openMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                },
                                blur: function() {
                                    var index =

                                    });

                                        model.closeMenu();
                                    }
                                    return;
                                }
                            }

<script>
                        window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = true;

                        require(['knockout'], function (ko) {
                            function register_custom_loader(component, vm_name, template_name) {
                                if (document.getElementById('template-' + (template_name || component) )) {
                                    var custom_loader = {
                                        getConfig: function(name, callback) {
                                            if (name === component + '-component') {
                                                componentConfig = {
                                                    template: { element: 'template-' + (template_name || component) },
                                                    viewModel: { require: 'components/' + (vm_name || component) }
                                                };
                                                callback(componentConfig);
                                            }
                                            else {
                                                callback(null)
                                            }
                                        }
                                    };

                                    ko.components.loaders.unshift(custom_loader);
                                }
                            }

                            register_custom_loader('ads', 'promotions', 'promotions');
                            register_custom_loader('dfp', 'evergreen', 'evergreen');

                            register_custom_loader('navigation');

                            
                            window.preloaded_templates_are_rendering = false;
                        });
                    </script>

<script>
    var host_element = document.querySelector(".b15ntl4ht-modal__text-host");
    host_element.href = window.location.href; 
    host_element.innerText = window.location.hostname; 

    function close_banner() {
        var CookieDate = new Date;
        CookieDate.setTime(CookieDate.getTime() + 1 * 3600 * 1000 * 24);
        document.cookie = "sidearm-adblock-banner_consent=true; expires=\"" + CookieDate.toGMTString() + "\";";
        document.querySelector(".b15ntl4ht").remove();
    }

    var consent_button = document.querySelector(".b15ntl4ht-banner__consent");

    consent_button.addEventListener("click", function() { close_banner(); });

    require(['config'], function(config) {
        require(['jquery', 'knockout', 'cookie', 'text'], function ($, ko, cookie, text) {
            $(function () {   
                //disable check for Siteimprove scans
                if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf('siteimprove') < 0) {
                    
                    if (cookie.get_cookie('sidearm-adblock-banner_consent')) {
                        return;
                    }

                    var deferred = $.Deferred();
                    $.ajax({
                        type: "HEAD",
                        async: true,
                        url: "/components/js/analytics.js",
                    }).done(function(message,text,jqXHR){
                        deferred.resolve();
                    })
                    .fail(function(err){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                        deferred.reject();
                    });

                    deferred.then(function(success) {
                        $.get('/common/templates/dfp/dfp-component-template.html')
                            .then(function (response) {
                            }, function (error) {
                                show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal();
                            });
                    }, function (error) {
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    })
                    .fail(function(){
                        show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal()
                    });

                    function show_ad_blocker_blocked_modal() {
                        var modal = document.querySelector('.b15ntl4ht');
                        modal.style.display = 'flex';
                        modal.querySelector('.b15ntl4ht-banner__consent').focus();
                    }
                }
            });
        });
    });
</script>

<script>
                    let $slick = document.querySelector('sidearm-accessible-slick-pause-all');
                    if ($slick) {
                       $slick.addEventListener('click', function(e) {
                           let $this = document.querySelector(this),
                               paused = $this.classList.contains('sidearm-paused'),
                               $slickSliders = document.querySelector('.slick-initialized'),
                               $pauseButtonsText = document.querySelector('.sidearm-accessible-pause-text'),
                               $jaws = $this.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.sidearm-jaws-talk-please')[0];

                           if (paused)
                           {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPlay');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.remove('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Pause All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Playing';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Pause';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           } else {
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickPause');
                               $slickSliders.slick('slickGoTo', 0, false);

                               $this.classList.add('sidearm-paused');
                               $this = 'Play All Rotators';
                               $jaws = 'All Rotators Paused';

                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'off');
                               $pauseButtonsText = 'Play';
                               $pauseButtonsText.setAttribute('aria-live', 'polite');
                           }
                       });
                    }
                </script>
